                            'Interferium' 1.0

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Interferium' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} where you have to connect all
tiles that are of the same type. To do so, you have to make a 'path'
from one tile and make your way to another tile. But beware, there
are some other tiles on the game board, so it is up to you to make
paths that will let the other tiles be connected without
interference...

  Complete each game board in the least amount of moves.

  Have fun!

